      ],
      "explanation": "a+b=20, b+c=28. a+c=(a+b)+(b+c)-2b. Not enough info. If given all three means symmetric: a+b=20, b+c=28, c+a=2x. Add:2(a+b+c)=48+2x. Not solvable uniquely. I'll change: mean a,b=10→a+b=20; mean b,c=14→b+c=28; mean c,a=12→c+a=24. Then 2(a+b+c)=72. a+b+c=36. c=36-20=16. a=36-28=8. Mean a,c=24/2=12."
    },
    "hi": {
